sentences.english: The last segment, in purple, is the Stack.
sentences.chinese: 最后一个紫色的段是堆栈。

sentences.english: Put in the stack, and grab cakes served in the three new mini games.
sentences.chinese: 放在堆栈，抢蛋糕服务三个新的迷你游戏。

sentences.english: These two request sequences emphasize different performance characteristics of web services stacks.
sentences.chinese: 这两个请求序列强调不同的网络服务堆栈的性能特点。

sentences.english: This is main string here on the stack.
sentences.chinese: 这个是在堆栈中的主字符串。

sentences.english: If the character is an operand, push it onto the stack.
sentences.chinese: 如果字符是一个操作数，把它压入堆栈。

sentences.english: The network stack, by design, follows a layered architecture modeled after the protocols themselves.
sentences.chinese: 网络堆栈在设计上遵循模拟协议本身的分层体系结构。

sentences.english: Today, most would agree that the bottom of the stack is solid.
sentences.chinese: 如今，大多数人都会同意，这个堆栈的基础是坚固的。

sentences.english: At the end of the postfix expression, pop a result from the stack.
sentences.chinese: 到后缀表达式末尾，从堆栈中弹出结果。

sentences.english: Additionally room of a car rents, can make goods warehouse.
sentences.chinese: 还有一个车房诚意出租，可作堆栈。

sentences.english: While stopped at a breakpoint, you can also inspect the execution stack.
sentences.chinese: 当在一个断点停止时，您还可以检查执行堆栈。

sentences.english: Like an appliance, the specific image stack is controlled and tested together.
sentences.chinese: 与设备类似，具体的映像堆栈集中控制和测试。

sentences.english: After some resources are added to the stack, the Back button becomes active.
sentences.chinese: 向堆栈中添加一些记录后，后退按钮就变成活动的了。

sentences.english: You can see a stack trace in the exception object.
sentences.chinese: 在这个异常对象内可以看到一个堆栈跟踪。

sentences.english: This provides a consistent experience in profile management for each product stack.
sentences.chinese: 这为每个产品堆栈提供了概要管理方面的一致体验。

sentences.english: The suite should "hit" the main components within each layer of the service stack.
sentences.chinese: 此套件应当适用于服务堆栈每层中的主要组件。
